Abstract = {European Law Enforcement Agencies are increasingly more reliant on
   information and communication technologies and are affected by a society
   shaped by the Internet and social media. The richness and quantity of
   information available from open sources, if properly gathered and
   processed, can provide valuable intelligence and help drawing inference
   from existing closed source intelligence. CAPER is an Open Source
   INTelligence platform for the prevention of organized crime, created in
   cooperation with European LEAs. CAPER supports information sharing and
