   artificial intelligence systems. This paper deals with the available
   intelligent data analysis in information security and the possibilities
   provided by data mining. Examples of tasks that can be solved using
   artificial intelligence systems are presented, including safe resource
   management, prediction of critical states and failures, resolution of
   conflicts in computational processes and information security
   regulations, and forensics.},
