   PEOPLES R CHINA, JUN 24-26, 2016},
Organization = {Tsinghua Univ; Inst Elect \& Elect Engineers; IEEE Syst; Chinese Univ
   Hong Kong; S China Univ Technol},
Abstract = {Sustainability is widely recognized as one of the most important
   challenges faced by the world. More and more companies have started
   publishing their sustain ability reports. This paper applies a text
   mining approach to discover sustain ability trends in the financial
   services sector using corporate sustainability reports. The findings of
   this paper demonstrate that client centricity, high governance,
   financial crime control, sustainable policies of mortgage and loan, and
   training and education are considered as important sustainability issues
   or concerns in financial services sector in Europe and North America.
   These insights can help financial institutions identify improvement
   opportunities by comparing its own sustain ability efforts with the
   overall trends in the financial services sector.},
