   Coimbra, Coimbra, PORTUGAL, SEP 08-11, 2015},
Organization = {Sistemas Cognitivos S A; Feedzai S A; Thinkware S A; iClio; FBA;
   Fundacao Ciencia Tecnologia},
Abstract = {Text Mining has opened a vast array of possibilities concerning
   automatic information retrieval from large amounts of text documents. A
   variety of themes and types of documents can be easily analyzed. More
   complex features such as those used in Forensic Linguistics can gather
   deeper understanding from the documents, making possible performing
   difficult tasks such as author identification. In this work we explore
   the capabilities of simpler Text Mining approaches to author
   identification of unstructured documents, in particular the ability to
   distinguish poetic works from two of Fernando Pessoas' heteronyms:
   `Alvaro de Campos and Ricardo Reis. Several processing options were
   tested and accuracies of 97\% were reached, which encourage further
   developments.},
